description:
Swisse Ultivite Men’s Multivitamin is a comprehensive multivitamin tailored for men. It supports general wellbeing, energy production and vitality.

Swisse Ultivite Men’s Multivitamin is scientifically formulated to provide a comprehensive blend of vitamins, minerals and herbs to support a healthy, active lifestyle. Tailored specifically for men, this multivitamin supports immune health and energy production, helps relieve fatigue, supports healthy muscle function and helps prevent dietary nutritional deficiencies.

Tailored for men to support general wellbeing.

Contains 45 vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, and herbs.

Supports healthy stress response in the body and mental function.

Supports energy production and vitality.
